      "raw_text": "INDIANAPOLIS, Aug. IA con-\nference believed to foreshadow the\naffiliation of the United Mine Work.\ners of America with the Western\nFederation of Miners is in progress\nhere today.\n\n\nPresident Samuel Gompers of the\nAmerican Federation of Labor, Pres\nident Moyar of the Western FEEDER\nGRAFTON of Miners, and Secretary\nMitchell, together with President\nO'Connell of the International Asso-\ncitation of Machinists and President\nHuber of the United Brotherhood OF\nCarpenters, met this morning and 1t\nwas intimated by Gompers that an\nagreement might be reached to-\nnight.\n\n\nPresident Lewis of the United\nMine Workers did not participate in\nthe conference, which is taken as\nindicating that he mineworkers are\nnot opposed to affiliation with the\nWestern Federation."
    }
